# Access Control Policy
## GeoMaps Consulting

### Purpose
To define how access to geospatial datasets and IT systems is granted, monitored, and revoked.

### Roles and Permissions

| Role    | Access Level                                           |
|---------|-------------------------------------------------------|
| Admin   | Full access to all datasets, servers, cloud storage. |
| Analyst | Access to datasets relevant to analytics only.       |
| Guest   | View-only access to selected datasets.               |

### Access Rules
1. Role-based access is mandatory; no shared credentials.  
2. High-risk datasets require additional approval for access.  
3. All access attempts are logged and reviewed monthly.  
4. Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) is required for Admin accounts.  
5. Temporary access for contractors must be approved and revoked after the project ends.

### Password Requirements
- Minimum 12 characters, mix of letters, numbers, symbols.  
- Change passwords every 90 days.  
- Never reuse previous passwords.
